ststructuralists" title="Category:Poststructuralists">Poststructuralists</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:Sociologists_of_science" title="Category:Sociologists of science">Sociologists of science</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:1930_births" title="Category:1930 births">1930 births</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:2002_deaths" title="Category:2002 deaths">2002 deaths</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:People_from_Pyr%C3%A9n%C3%A9es-Atlantiques" title="Category:People from Pyrénées-Atlantiques">People from Pyrénées-Atlantiques</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:Burials_at_P%C3%A8re_Lachaise_Cemetery" title="Category:Burials at Père Lachaise Cemetery">Burials at Père Lachaise Cemetery</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:French_military_personnel_of_the_Algerian_War" title="Category:French military personnel of the Algerian War">French military personnel of the Algerian War</a></span></div><div id="mw-hidden-catlinks" class="mw-hidden-cats-hidden">Hidden categories:&#32;<span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:Cleanup_from_March_2008" title="Category:Cleanup from March 2008">Cleanup from March 2008</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:Wikipedia_articles_needing_style_editing_from_March_2008" title="Category:Wikipedia articles needing style editing from March 2008">Wikipedia articles needing style editing from March 2008</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:All_articles_needing_style_editing" title="Category:All articles needing style editing">All articles needing style editing</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:Articles_needing_additional_references_from_August_2007" title="Category:Articles needing additional references from August 2007">Articles needing additional references from August 2007</a></span></div></div>			<!-- end content -->
